Package presentationLayer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllCalculations
    Shows all gets all calculations from the database, so it can be displayed on allcalculations.jsp
    AllRequests
    Gets all orders/requests from the database to be displayed on ordermanagement.jsp.
    BackToOrders
    Removes the session attibutes used when viewing a request in viewbom.jsp.
    CustomerView
    Retrieves all orders/requests, that the customer currently logged in has in the database.
    DeleteEmployee
    Used to display all employees and potentially delete one.
    EditRequest
    Updates a request in the database.
    EditTotalPrice
    Updates the totalprice of a request in the database.
    FrontController
    Before going to a new jsp-page, everything goes here to execute a new servlet.
    InputCarport
    All input from the index carport calculation is processed here.
    Login
    Gives the possibillity to login as employee or customer.
    LogReader
    All logs are fetched and put into a list to be shown on logging.jsp.
    Navbar
    Directs the user to the desired jsp-page.
    PayForOrder
    Updates the order to "paid" in the database.
    RegisterCustomer
    Inserts a new customer into the database.
    RegisterEmployee
    Inserts a new employee to the database.
    SendRequest
    Inserts the request into the database.
    SetOrdered
    After reviewing the request, the Bill of Material is inserted into the database.
    UnknownCommand
    Used if a Command/servlet cannot be found in the Command class.
    UpdateQuantityBom
    Updates the quantity of the given product.
    ViewBom
    Retrieves the request from the database and calculates a bill of material.
    ViewFinalBom
    Retrieves the final bill of material, which is now in the database.
